I did not get his contact details from the clinic nor could I find his contact details on the Internet. So, I started visiting other dentists for my dental issues, but could not find any Dentist who gave the treatment like Dr Chiranjeevi Reddy. So I decided to look for Dr Chiranjeevi Reddy again.

1.	His staff is very courteous and as professional as Dr Reddy

This clinic is ideal for anyone having Dental issues and I strongly recommend you consider this clinic for your dental treatment.
